what are the ad pic dimensions for pictures and videos?

For NewsBreak ads, the supported dimensions for images and videos are 9x16 (vertical) and 16x9 (horizontal). Video ads can be up to a minute long. It's recommended to separate video ads and images into different ad sets for optimal performance.
what is the recommended memory size?

The recommended memory size for creatives isn't specified in terms of file size, but it's important to ensure that your video and image files are optimized for quick loading and high quality. Generally, keeping the file size as small as possible without compromising quality is a good practice.
